---
source: tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
Manage projects

Usage: mf project [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  new      Create a project
  list     List projects [aliases: ls]
  archive  Archive a project
  lint     Lint a project
  index    Index projects
  show     Show project details
  import   Import a directory as a project
  rename   Rename a project
  remove   Remove a project [aliases: rm]

Options:
      --root <PATH>
          Mind Repo root directory
      --config <PATH>
          Config file path
  -v, --verbose...
          Verbose output
  -q, --quiet
          Silence non-error output
      --format <FORMAT>
          Output format [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --json
          Shorthand for --format json
      --no-color
          Disable colored output
  -p, --project <NAME>
          Project name for project-scoped operations
      --install-completion <INSTALL_COMPLETION>
          Install shell completion script [possible values: bash, zsh, fish, powershell, elvish]
      --show-completion <SHOW_COMPLETION>
          Show shell completion script [possible values: bash, zsh, fish, powershell, elvish]
  -h, --help
          Print help
  -V, --version
          Print version
